P82_BatteryStatus
public static class P82_BatteryStatus.P82_BatteryStatus_CachedDecoder
extends java.lang.Object

This object will decode the page and cache the decoded results in the associated fields. It is useful for external use when this page needs to be decoded without using the event based system.

cumulativeOperatingTime

public long cumulativeOperatingTime
The cumulative operating time since the battery was inserted. Units: seconds (resolution indicated by cumulativeOperatingTimeResolution]). Rollover: Every 16777215s*resolution. ie:~1.1yrs at 2s resolution, ~8.5yrs at 16s resolution.
